The state forcefully acquired the facility for the expansion of Uhuru Highway and construction of a bus terminus.
Mwamba are now actively looking for a home ground. I understand they have been pursuing several options around Upper Hill, Parklands, Ngong Road and other areas, all within Nairobi County.
It is a throwback to 1978 when Mwamba was founded. Mwamba’s formation was steeped in African idealism and the desire for social, racial and economic equality, not to mention national pride.



